<div >
  <div class="main_page_search_container" flex  ng-cloak>


    <div class="white_text center_text" layout="row" layout-align="center"  >
      <h1><span class="header_font">Learn Your Lesson</span> 
        <p hide-gt-xs >is your place to connect with local teachers <span hide-xs> on languages, music lessons,<br> or any other skill you wish to learn
<div ></p>
        <p hide-xs class="reduced_header_font">is your place to connect with local teachers on languages,<br> music lessons, or any other skill you wish to learn</p> </span>
       
      </h1>
    </div> <!-- end of white_text -->

    <form  layout="row" layout-align="center center" name="search_form" flex>          
          
        
      <div layout="row" layout-xs="column">
        <div flex>
            <md-autocomplete 
              md-select-on-match
              md-autoselect
              id="select_subject"
              class="black_text subject_search"
              md-selected-item="selected.subject_name" 
              md-input-name="subject"
              md-search-text="searchText.subject_name"
              md-search-text-change="search_subjects( searchText.subject_name )"
              md-items="subject in subjects_list" 
              md-item-text="subject"            
              md-selected-item-change="subject_picked( subject )"
              ng-model-options="{ debounce: 500 }"
              placeholder="Subject?"
              md-min-length="2">
            <md-item-template>
              <span md-highlight-text="searchText">{{subject}}</span>
            </md-item-template>
            <div ng-messages="search_form.subject.$error">
              <div ng-message="required">This is required</div>
              <div ng-message="no_select">Please click one of the provied options</div>
            </div>
            <md-not-found>
              No matches found.
            </md-not-found>
          </md-autocomplete>

        </div>

        <div  layout-align="center center" class="county_search" flex>
          <md-autocomplete 
              class="black_text subject_search"
              md-selected-item="selected.county_name" 
              md-input-name="county"
              md-search-text="searchText.county_name" 
              md-items="county in counties" 
              md-item-text="county" 
              md-search-text-change="search_counties( searchText.county_name )"
              placeholder="County?"
              md-selected-item-change="county_picked( county )">
            <md-item-template>
              <span md-highlight-text="county">{{county}}</span>
            </md-item-template>
            
          </md-autocomplete>    
        </div>

        
      </div> <!-- end of row -->   
    </form> <!-- end of search() -->
    <div layout="row" layout-align="center center" flex>
      <md-button ng-click="search()" class="md-raised md-primary icon_button white_text">Search<i class="material-icons">search</i></md-button>
    </div> <!-- end of row -->

    
    
  </div> <!-- end of main_page_search_container -->
  <div class="center_text">
    <md-button ui-sref="register_teacher" class="md-raised blue_button">Become a teacher</md-button>
  </div>
  <div layout="row"  layout-margin-gt-xs flex >
    
    <md-content class="grey_green_background how_it_works" >
      <div layout="column" class="center_text">
        <h1 class="green_text" flex="100">How it works</h1><br><br>
        <h4 flex="100">From finding the perfect teacher to managing bookings and scheduling lessons - we take care of all the details, so you can focus on learning. <a ui-sref="how_it_works"></a></h4> <br>
      </div>
      <div layout="row" layout-xs="column" >
        
        <div class="center_text " flex>
          <%= image_tag 'search_for_a_teacher.jpg' %>
          <h3>Search for your teacher</h3>
          Compare teachers based on the criteria that matter to to you -from age and location to experience and price.
        </div> <!-- end of col-xs-4 -->

        <div class="center_text " flex>
          <%= image_tag 'schedule_your_lessons.jpg' %>
          <h3>Schedule your lessons</h3>
          When you've found your preferred teacher, schedule your lessons via direct email with the teacher
          deposit to confirm the lesson.
        </div> <!-- end of col-xs-4 -->

        <div class="center_text " flex>
          <%= image_tag 'connect_with_your_teacher.jpg' %>
          <h3>Connect with your teacher</h3>
          On the scheduled date and at the agreed venue - you can meet your teacher and learn your lesson. 
        </div> <!-- end of col-xs-4 -->
      </div>
      
      
    </md-content>
   
  </div> <!-- end of flex -->
  <div class="center_text">
    <md-button ui-sref="register_teacher" class="md-raised blue_button">Become a teacher</md-button>
  </div>
  <div flex class="x_large_font animateblock btm anchor1" style="max-width:100vw !important;">
    <div layout="row" flex="100">
      <md-content layout-margin-gt-xs class="center_text pale_orange_background">
        <h1><strong>Are you a teacher?</strong></h1>
        <p>Learn your lesson can help you grow the number of students you teach - whilst helping you manage your teaching schedules and incoming finances. </p>
        <%= image_tag 'are_you_a_teacher_list_left.jpg', class: "flex-100 flex-xs-50" %>
        <%= image_tag 'are_you_a_teacher_list_right.jpg', class: "flex-100 flex-xs-50" %>
        <p>As a teacher you know that teachers face the battle of finding new students. Now, did you know that everyday students also face the battle of finding teachers?</p><br><br>
        
      </md-content> <!-- end of are_you_a_teacher -->
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="center_text">
    <md-button ui-sref="register_teacher" class="md-raised blue_button">Become a teacher</md-button>
  </div>
  <div flex class="x_large_font animateblock centerright anchor2" style="max-width:100vw !important;">
    <div layout="row" flex="100">
      <md-content layout-margin-gt-xs class="center_text pale_orange_background">
        <p>Well, call us the middle man. We have built a platform that students rely on to find teachers and we help teachers get more students without having to invest time and money on marketing. With a free profile on LearnYourLesson.ie, your skills will be visible to the students who search our site every day for teachers like you. And with mobile optimisation you'll extend your reach even further.</p>


        <div >
          <div >
            <h3 ><strong>Free Profile</strong></h3>
            <p>Extend your reach to thousands of students actively searching for teachers like you</p>
          </div> <!-- end of are_you_a_teacher_container -->

          <div >
            <h3 ><strong>National Reach</strong></h3>
            <p>Use our reach to connect with students anywhere in Ireland through live, online lessons.</p>
          </div> <!-- end of are_you_a_teacher_container -->

          <div >
            <h3 ><strong>Risk-Free</strong></h3>
            <p>Get started today for free.</p>
          </div> <!-- end of are_you_a_teacher_container -->

          <div>
            <h3 ><strong>Manage Your Business</strong></h3>
            <p>With LearnYourLesson, you can manage your lessons, earnings, and more all in one place. With our platform you can reset the balance of power: more teaching, less administration. You can personalise your prices, teaching instruments, location and lesson duration.</p>
          </div> <!-- end of are_you_a_teacher_container -->

          <div class="center_text">
            <md-button ui-sref="register_teacher" class="md-raised blue_button">Become a teacher</md-button>
          </div>

        </div> <!-- end of are_you_a_teacher -->
      </md-content>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> <!-- end of column -->


